text: Poliaenus concolor is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Schaeffer in 1909. It is known from Baja California.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus concolor. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1909
title: Poliaenus concolor
